# Package dev loop

Follow `AGENTS.md` and `docs/architecture.md`. Target: SDK `AgentTool[]` + skill → `systemPrompt`.

When editing `packages/<name>/` (not `_template`):

1. `pnpm run validate`
2. `pnpm run typecheck`
3. Unit-test tool `execute` paths without an LLM where possible
4. Optional CLI debug: `pi --skill ./skills/<name> -e ./extensions/...` (dev only)
5. Optional: `pnpm run smoke -- <name>` or task **Pi Agents: Smoke Agent**

Register new agents in `registry/agents.ts` when it exists. Harness integration tests run in consumer repos.
